title: Hour 1 - Walking Aaron Judge, Al Leiter
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Walking Aaron Judge, Al Leiter
description:
Dan worries that nobody will pitch to Yankees slugger Aaron Judge for the rest of the season and he won't hit any more homeruns. And MLB insider Al Leiter weighs in on exactly why Judge isn't seeing any good pitches.
